{"tha-ap3:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap3:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap3:0.3":"Sariputtattheraapadana ","tha-ap3:1.1":"Atha therapadanam sunatha—","tha-ap3:2.1":"“Himavantassa avidure, ","tha-ap3:2.2":"lambako nama pabbato; ","tha-ap3:2.3":"Assamo sukato mayham, ","tha-ap3:2.4":"pannasala sumapita. ","tha-ap3:3.1":"Uttanakula nadika, ","tha-ap3:3.2":"supatittha manorama; ","tha-ap3:3.3":"Susuddhapulinakinna, ","tha-ap3:3.4":"avidure mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:4.1":"Asakkhara apabbhara, ","tha-ap3:4.2":"sadu appatigandhika; ","tha-ap3:4.3":"Sandati nadika tattha, ","tha-ap3:4.4":"sobhayanta mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:5.1":"Kumbhila makara cettha, ","tha-ap3:5.2":"susumara ca kacchapa; ","tha-ap3:5.3":"Caranti nadiya tattha, ","tha-ap3:5.4":"sobhayanta mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:6.1":"Pathina pavusa maccha, ","tha-ap3:6.2":"balaja munjarohita; ","tha-ap3:6.3":"Vaggala papatayanta, ","tha-ap3:6.4":"sobhayanti mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:7.1":"Ubho kulesu nadiya, ","tha-ap3:7.2":"pupphino phalino duma; ","tha-ap3:7.3":"Ubhato abhilambanta, ","tha-ap3:7.4":"sobhayanti mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:8.1":"Amba sala ca tilaka, ","tha-ap3:8.2":"patali sinduvaraka; ","tha-ap3:8.3":"Dibbagandha sampavanti, ","tha-ap3:8.4":"pupphita mama assame. ","tha-ap3:9.1":"Campaka salala nipa, ","tha-ap3:9.2":"nagapunnagaketaka; ","tha-ap3:9.3":"Dibbagandha sampavanti, ","tha-ap3:9.4":"pupphita mama assame. ","tha-ap3:10.1":"Atimutta asoka ca, ","tha-ap3:10.2":"bhaginimala ca pupphita; ","tha-ap3:10.3":"Ankola bimbijala ca, ","tha-ap3:10.4":"pupphita mama assame. ","tha-ap3:11.1":"Ketaka kandali ceva, ","tha-ap3:11.2":"godhuka tinasulika; ","tha-ap3:11.3":"Dibbagandham sampavanta, ","tha-ap3:11.4":"sobhayanti mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:12.1":"Kanikara kannika ca, ","tha-ap3:12.2":"asana ajjuna bahu; ","tha-ap3:12.3":"Dibbagandham sampavanta, ","tha-ap3:12.4":"sobhayanti mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:13.1":"Punnaga giripunnaga, ","tha-ap3:13.2":"kovilara ca pupphita; ","tha-ap3:13.3":"Dibbagandham sampavanta, ","tha-ap3:13.4":"sobhayanti mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:14.1":"Uddhalaka ca kutaja, ","tha-ap3:14.2":"kadamba vakula bahu; ","tha-ap3:14.3":"Dibbagandham sampavanta, ","tha-ap3:14.4":"sobhayanti mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:15.1":"Alaka isimugga ca, ","tha-ap3:15.2":"kadalimatulungiyo; ","tha-ap3:15.3":"Gandhodakena samvaddha, ","tha-ap3:15.4":"phalani dharayanti te. ","tha-ap3:16.1":"Anne pupphanti paduma, ","tha-ap3:16.2":"anne jayanti kesari; ","tha-ap3:16.3":"Anne opuppha paduma, ","tha-ap3:16.4":"pupphita talake tada. ","tha-ap3:17.1":"Gabbham ganhanti paduma, ","tha-ap3:17.2":"niddhavanti mulaliyo; ","tha-ap3:17.3":"Singhatipattamakinna, ","tha-ap3:17.4":"sobhanti talake tada. ","tha-ap3:18.1":"Nayita ambagandhi ca, ","tha-ap3:18.2":"uttali bandhujivaka; ","tha-ap3:18.3":"Dibbagandha sampavanti, ","tha-ap3:18.4":"pupphita talake tada. ","tha-ap3:19.1":"Pathina pavusa maccha, ","tha-ap3:19.2":"balaja munjarohita; ","tha-ap3:19.3":"Sangula maggura ceva, ","tha-ap3:19.4":"vasanti talake tada. ","tha-ap3:20.1":"Kumbhila susumara ca, ","tha-ap3:20.2":"tantigaha ca rakkhasa; ","tha-ap3:20.3":"Oguha ajagara ca, ","tha-ap3:20.4":"vasanti talake tada. ","tha-ap3:21.1":"Parevata ravihamsa, ","tha-ap3:21.2":"cakkavaka nadicara; ","tha-ap3:21.3":"Kokila sukasalika, ","tha-ap3:21.4":"upajivanti tam saram. ","tha-ap3:22.1":"Kukkutthaka kuliraka, ","tha-ap3:22.2":"vane pokkharasataka; ","tha-ap3:22.3":"Dindibha suvapota ca, ","tha-ap3:22.4":"upajivanti tam saram. ","tha-ap3:23.1":"Hamsa konca mayura ca, ","tha-ap3:23.2":"kokila tambaculaka; ","tha-ap3:23.3":"Pammaka jivamjiva ca, ","tha-ap3:23.4":"upajivanti tam saram. ","tha-ap3:24.1":"Kosika potthasisa ca, ","tha-ap3:24.2":"kurara senaka bahu; ","tha-ap3:24.3":"Mahakala ca sakuna, ","tha-ap3:24.4":"upajivanti tam saram. ","tha-ap3:25.1":"Pasada ca varaha ca, ","tha-ap3:25.2":"camara gandaka bahu; ","tha-ap3:25.3":"Rohicca sukapota ca, ","tha-ap3:25.4":"upajivanti tam saram. ","tha-ap3:26.1":"Sihabyaggha ca dipi ca, ","tha-ap3:26.2":"acchakokataracchaka; ","tha-ap3:26.3":"Tidha pabhinnamatanga, ","tha-ap3:26.4":"upajivanti tam saram. ","tha-ap3:27.1":"Kinnara vanara ceva, ","tha-ap3:27.2":"athopi vanakammika; ","tha-ap3:27.3":"Ceta ca luddaka ceva, ","tha-ap3:27.4":"upajivanti tam saram. ","tha-ap3:28.1":"Tindukani piyalani, ","tha-ap3:28.2":"madhuke kasumariyo; ","tha-ap3:28.3":"Dhuvam phalani dharenti, ","tha-ap3:28.4":"avidure mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:29.1":"Kosamba salala nimba, ","tha-ap3:29.2":"saduphalasamayuta; ","tha-ap3:29.3":"Dhuvam phalani dharenti, ","tha-ap3:29.4":"avidure mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:30.1":"Haritaka amalaka, ","tha-ap3:30.2":"ambajambuvibhitaka; ","tha-ap3:30.3":"Kola bhallataka billa, ","tha-ap3:30.4":"phalani dharayanti te. ","tha-ap3:31.1":"Aluva ca kalamba ca, ","tha-ap3:31.2":"bilalitakkalani ca; ","tha-ap3:31.3":"Jivaka sutaka ceva, ","tha-ap3:31.4":"bahuka mama assame. ","tha-ap3:32.1":"Assamassaviduramhi, ","tha-ap3:32.2":"talakasum sunimmita; ","tha-ap3:32.3":"Acchodaka sitajala, ","tha-ap3:32.4":"supatittha manorama. ","tha-ap3:33.1":"Padumuppalasanchanna, ","tha-ap3:33.2":"pundarikasamayuta; ","tha-ap3:33.3":"Mandalakehi sanchanna, ","tha-ap3:33.4":"dibbagandho pavayati. ","tha-ap3:34.1":"Evam sabbangasampanne, ","tha-ap3:34.2":"pupphite phalite vane; ","tha-ap3:34.3":"Sukate assame ramme, ","tha-ap3:34.4":"viharami aham tada. ","tha-ap3:35.1":"Silava vatasampanno, ","tha-ap3:35.2":"jhayi jhanarato sada; ","tha-ap3:35.3":"Pancabhinnabalappatto, ","tha-ap3:35.4":"suruci nama tapaso. ","tha-ap3:36.1":"Catuvisasahassani, ","tha-ap3:36.2":"sissa mayham upatthahum; ","tha-ap3:36.3":"Sabbeva brahmana ete, ","tha-ap3:36.4":"jatimanto yasassino. ","tha-ap3:37.1":"Lakkhane itihase ca, ","tha-ap3:37.2":"sanighantusaketubhe; ","tha-ap3:37.3":"Padaka veyyakarana, ","tha-ap3:37.4":"sadhamme paramim gata. ","tha-ap3:38.1":"Uppatesu nimittesu, ","tha-ap3:38.2":"lakkhanesu ca kovida; ","tha-ap3:38.3":"Pathabya bhumantalikkhe, ","tha-ap3:38.4":"mama sissa susikkhita. ","tha-ap3:39.1":"Appiccha nipaka ete, ","tha-ap3:39.2":"appahara alolupa; ","tha-ap3:39.3":"Labhalabhena santuttha, ","tha-ap3:39.4":"parivarenti mam sada. ","tha-ap3:40.1":"Jhayi jhanarata dhira, ","tha-ap3:40.2":"santacitta samahita; ","tha-ap3:40.3":"Akincannam patthayanta, ","tha-ap3:40.4":"parivarenti mam sada. ","tha-ap3:41.1":"Abhinnaparamippatta, ","tha-ap3:41.2":"pettike gocare rata; ","tha-ap3:41.3":"Antalikkhacara dhira, ","tha-ap3:41.4":"parivarenti mam sada. ","tha-ap3:42.1":"Samvuta chasu dvaresu, ","tha-ap3:42.2":"aneja rakkhitindriya; ","tha-ap3:42.3":"Asamsattha ca te dhira, ","tha-ap3:42.4":"mama sissa durasada. ","tha-ap3:43.1":"Pallankena nisajjaya, ","tha-ap3:43.2":"thanacankamanena ca; ","tha-ap3:43.3":"Vitinamenti te rattim, ","tha-ap3:43.4":"mama sissa durasada. ","tha-ap3:44.1":"Rajaniye na rajjanti, ","tha-ap3:44.2":"dussaniye na dussare; ","tha-ap3:44.3":"Mohaniye na muyhanti, ","tha-ap3:44.4":"mama sissa durasada. ","tha-ap3:45.1":"Iddhim vimamsamana te, ","tha-ap3:45.2":"vattanti niccakalikam; ","tha-ap3:45.3":"Pathavim te pakampenti, ","tha-ap3:45.4":"sarambhena durasada. ","tha-ap3:46.1":"Kilamana ca te sissa, ","tha-ap3:46.2":"kilanti jhanakilitam; ","tha-ap3:46.3":"Jambuto phalamanenti, ","tha-ap3:46.4":"mama sissa durasada. ","tha-ap3:47.1":"Anne gacchanti goyanam, ","tha-ap3:47.2":"anne pubbavidehakam; ","tha-ap3:47.3":"Anne ca uttarakurum, ","tha-ap3:47.4":"esanaya durasada. ","tha-ap3:48.1":"Purato pesenti kharim, ","tha-ap3:48.2":"pacchato ca vajanti te; ","tha-ap3:48.3":"Catuvisasahassehi, ","tha-ap3:48.4":"chaditam hoti ambaram. ","tha-ap3:49.1":"Aggipaki anaggi ca, ","tha-ap3:49.2":"dantodukkhalikapi ca; ","tha-ap3:49.3":"Asmena kottita keci, ","tha-ap3:49.4":"pavattaphalabhojana. ","tha-ap3:50.1":"Udakorohana keci, ","tha-ap3:50.2":"sayam pato sucirata; ","tha-ap3:50.3":"Toyabhisecanakara, ","tha-ap3:50.4":"mama sissa durasada. ","tha-ap3:51.1":"Parulhakacchanakhaloma, ","tha-ap3:51.2":"pankadanta rajassira; ","tha-ap3:51.3":"Gandhita silagandhena, ","tha-ap3:51.4":"mama sissa durasada. ","tha-ap3:52.1":"Patova sannipatitva, ","tha-ap3:52.2":"jatila uggatapana; ","tha-ap3:52.3":"Labhalabham pakittetva, ","tha-ap3:52.4":"gacchanti ambare tada. ","tha-ap3:53.1":"Etesam pakkamantanam, ","tha-ap3:53.2":"mahasaddo pavattati; ","tha-ap3:53.3":"Ajinacammasaddena, ","tha-ap3:53.4":"mudita honti devata. ","tha-ap3:54.1":"Disodisam pakkamanti, ","tha-ap3:54.2":"antalikkhacara isi; ","tha-ap3:54.3":"Sake balenupatthaddha, ","tha-ap3:54.4":"te gacchanti yadicchakam. ","tha-ap3:55.1":"Pathavikampaka ete, ","tha-ap3:55.2":"sabbeva nabhacarino; ","tha-ap3:55.3":"Uggateja duppasaha, ","tha-ap3:55.4":"sagarova akhobhiya. ","tha-ap3:56.1":"Thanacankamino keci, ","tha-ap3:56.2":"keci nesajjika isi; ","tha-ap3:56.3":"Pavattabhojana keci, ","tha-ap3:56.4":"mama sissa durasada. ","tha-ap3:57.1":"Mettaviharino ete, ","tha-ap3:57.2":"hitesi sabbapaninam; ","tha-ap3:57.3":"Anattukkamsaka sabbe, ","tha-ap3:57.4":"na te vambhenti kassaci. ","tha-ap3:58.1":"Siharajavasambhita, ","tha-ap3:58.2":"gajarajava thamava; ","tha-ap3:58.3":"Durasada byagghariva, ","tha-ap3:58.4":"agacchanti mamantike. ","tha-ap3:59.1":"Vijjadhara devata ca, ","tha-ap3:59.2":"nagagandhabbarakkhasa; ","tha-ap3:59.3":"Kumbhanda danava garula, ","tha-ap3:59.4":"upajivanti tam saram. ","tha-ap3:60.1":"Te jatakharibharita, ","tha-ap3:60.2":"ajinuttaravasana; ","tha-ap3:60.3":"Antalikkhacara sabbe, ","tha-ap3:60.4":"upajivanti tam saram. ","tha-ap3:61.1":"Sadanucchavika ete, ","tha-ap3:61.2":"annamannam sagarava; ","tha-ap3:61.3":"Catubbisasahassanam, ","tha-ap3:61.4":"khipitasaddo na vijjati. ","tha-ap3:62.1":"Pade padam nikkhipanta, ","tha-ap3:62.2":"appasadda susamvuta; ","tha-ap3:62.3":"Upasankamma sabbeva, ","tha-ap3:62.4":"sirasa vandare mamam. ","tha-ap3:63.1":"Tehi sissehi parivuto, ","tha-ap3:63.2":"santehi ca tapassibhi; ","tha-ap3:63.3":"Vasami assame tattha, ","tha-ap3:63.4":"jhayi jhanarato aham. ","tha-ap3:64.1":"Isinam silagandhena, ","tha-ap3:64.2":"pupphagandhena cubhayam; ","tha-ap3:64.3":"Phalinam phalagandhena, ","tha-ap3:64.4":"gandhito hoti assamo. ","tha-ap3:65.1":"Rattindivam na janami, ","tha-ap3:65.2":"arati me na vijjati; ","tha-ap3:65.3":"Sake sisse ovadanto, ","tha-ap3:65.4":"bhiyyo hasam labhamaham. ","tha-ap3:66.1":"Pupphanam pupphamananam, ","tha-ap3:66.2":"phalananca vipaccatam; ","tha-ap3:66.3":"Dibbagandha pavayanti, ","tha-ap3:66.4":"sobhayanta mamassamam. ","tha-ap3:67.1":"Samadhimha vutthahitva, ","tha-ap3:67.2":"atapi nipako aham; ","tha-ap3:67.3":"Kharibharam gahetvana, ","tha-ap3:67.4":"vanam ajjhogahim aham. ","tha-ap3:68.1":"Uppate supine capi, ","tha-ap3:68.2":"Lakkhanesu susikkhito; ","tha-ap3:68.3":"Pavattamanam mantapadam, ","tha-ap3:68.4":"Dharayami aham tada. ","tha-ap3:69.1":"Anomadassi bhagava, ","tha-ap3:69.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap3:69.3":"Vivekakamo sambuddho, ","tha-ap3:69.4":"himavantamupagami. ","tha-ap3:70.1":"Ajjhogahetva himavantam, ","tha-ap3:70.2":"aggo karuniko muni; ","tha-ap3:70.3":"Pallankam abhujitvana, ","tha-ap3:70.4":"nisidi purisuttamo. ","tha-ap3:71.1":"Tamaddasaham sambuddham, ","tha-ap3:71.2":"sappabhasam manoramam; ","tha-ap3:71.3":"Indivaramva jalitam, ","tha-ap3:71.4":"adittamva hutasanam. ","tha-ap3:72.1":"Jalantam diparukkhamva, ","tha-ap3:72.2":"vijjutam gagane yatha; ","tha-ap3:72.3":"Suphullam salarajamva, ","tha-ap3:72.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap3:73.1":"Ayam nago mahaviro, ","tha-ap3:73.2":"dukkhassantakaro muni; ","tha-ap3:73.3":"Imam dassanamagamma, ","tha-ap3:73.4":"sabbadukkha pamuccare. ","tha-ap3:74.1":"Disvanaham devadevam, ","tha-ap3:74.2":"lakkhanam upadharayim; ","tha-ap3:74.3":"Buddho nu kho na va buddho, ","tha-ap3:74.4":"handa passami cakkhumam. ","tha-ap3:75.1":"Sahassarani cakkani, ","tha-ap3:75.2":"dissanti caranuttame; ","tha-ap3:75.3":"Lakkhananissa disvana, ","tha-ap3:75.4":"nittham gacchim tathagate. ","tha-ap3:76.1":"Sammajjanim gahetvana, ","tha-ap3:76.2":"sammajjitvanaham tada; ","tha-ap3:76.3":"Atha pupphe samanetva, ","tha-ap3:76.4":"buddhasettham apujayim. ","tha-ap3:77.1":"Pujayitvana tam buddham, ","tha-ap3:77.2":"oghatinnamanasavam; ","tha-ap3:77.3":"Ekamsam ajinam katva, ","tha-ap3:77.4":"namassim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap3:78.1":"Yena nanena sambuddho, ","tha-ap3:78.2":"viharati anasavo; ","tha-ap3:78.3":"Tam nanam kittayissami, ","tha-ap3:78.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap3:79.1":"‘Samuddharasimam lokam, ","tha-ap3:79.2":"sayambhu amitodaya; ","tha-ap3:79.3":"Tava dassanamagamma, ","tha-ap3:79.4":"kankhasotam taranti te. ","tha-ap3:80.1":"Tuvam sattha ca ketu ca, ","tha-ap3:80.2":"dhajo yupo ca paninam; ","tha-ap3:80.3":"Parayano patittha ca, ","tha-ap3:80.4":"dipo ca dvipaduttamo. ","tha-ap3:81.1":"Sakka samudde udakam, ","tha-ap3:81.2":"pametum alhakena va; ","tha-ap3:81.3":"Na tveva tava sabbannu, ","tha-ap3:81.4":"nanam sakka pametave. ","tha-ap3:82.1":"Dharetum pathavim sakka, ","tha-ap3:82.2":"thapetva tulamandale; ","tha-ap3:82.3":"Na tveva tava sabbannu, ","tha-ap3:82.4":"nanam sakka dharetave. ","tha-ap3:83.1":"Akaso minitum sakka, ","tha-ap3:83.2":"rajjuya angulena va; ","tha-ap3:83.3":"Na tveva tava sabbannu, ","tha-ap3:83.4":"nanam sakka pametave. ","tha-ap3:84.1":"Mahasamudde udakam, ","tha-ap3:84.2":"pathavi cakhilajatam; ","tha-ap3:84.3":"Buddhananam upadaya, ","tha-ap3:84.4":"upamato na yujjare. ","tha-ap3:85.1":"Sadevakassa lokassa, ","tha-ap3:85.2":"cittam yesam pavattati; ","tha-ap3:85.3":"Antojalagata ete, ","tha-ap3:85.4":"tava nanamhi cakkhuma. ","tha-ap3:86.1":"Yena nanena pattosi, ","tha-ap3:86.2":"kevalam bodhimuttamam; ","tha-ap3:86.3":"Tena nanena sabbannu, ","tha-ap3:86.4":"maddasi paratitthiye’. ","tha-ap3:87.1":"Ima gatha thavitvana, ","tha-ap3:87.2":"suruci nama tapaso; ","tha-ap3:87.3":"Ajinam pattharitvana, ","tha-ap3:87.4":"pathaviyam nisidi so. ","tha-ap3:88.1":"‘Cullasitisahassani, ","tha-ap3:88.2":"ajjhogalho mahannave; ","tha-ap3:88.3":"Accuggato tavadeva, ","tha-ap3:88.4":"giriraja pavuccati. ","tha-ap3:89.1":"Tava accuggato neru, ","tha-ap3:89.2":"ayato vitthato ca so; ","tha-ap3:89.3":"Cunnito anubhedena, ","tha-ap3:89.4":"kotisatasahassaso. ","tha-ap3:90.1":"Lakkhe thapiyamanamhi, ","tha-ap3:90.2":"parikkhayamagacchatha; ","tha-ap3:90.3":"Na tveva tava sabbannu, ","tha-ap3:90.4":"nanam sakka pametave. ","tha-ap3:91.1":"Sukhumacchikena jalena, ","tha-ap3:91.2":"udakam yo parikkhipe; ","tha-ap3:91.3":"Ye keci udake pana, ","tha-ap3:91.4":"antojalagata siyum. ","tha-ap3:92.1":"Tatheva hi mahavira, ","tha-ap3:92.2":"ye keci puthutitthiya; ","tha-ap3:92.3":"Ditthigahanapakkhanda, ","tha-ap3:92.4":"paramasena mohita. ","tha-ap3:93.1":"Tava suddhena nanena, ","tha-ap3:93.2":"anavaranadassina; ","tha-ap3:93.3":"Antojalagata ete, ","tha-ap3:93.4":"nanam te nativattare’. ","tha-ap3:94.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap3:94.2":"anomadassi mahayaso; ","tha-ap3:94.3":"Vutthahitva samadhimha, ","tha-ap3:94.4":"disam olokayi jino. ","tha-ap3:95.1":"Anomadassimunino, ","tha-ap3:95.2":"Nisabho nama savako; ","tha-ap3:95.3":"Parivuto satasahassehi, ","tha-ap3:95.4":"Santacittehi tadibhi. ","tha-ap3:96.1":"Khinasavehi suddhehi, ","tha-ap3:96.2":"chalabhinnehi jhayibhi; ","tha-ap3:96.3":"Cittamannaya buddhassa, ","tha-ap3:96.4":"upesi lokanayakam. ","tha-ap3:97.1":"Antalikkhe thita tattha, ","tha-ap3:97.2":"padakkhinamakamsu te; ","tha-ap3:97.3":"Namassanta panjalika, ","tha-ap3:97.4":"otarum buddhasantike. ","tha-ap3:98.1":"Anomadassi bhagava, ","tha-ap3:98.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap3:98.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap3:98.4":"sitam patukari jino. ","tha-ap3:99.1":"Varuno namupatthako, ","tha-ap3:99.2":"anomadassissa satthuno; ","tha-ap3:99.3":"Ekamsam civaram katva, ","tha-ap3:99.4":"apucchi lokanayakam. ","tha-ap3:100.1":"‘Ko nu kho bhagava hetu, ","tha-ap3:100.2":"sitakammassa satthuno; ","tha-ap3:100.3":"Na hi buddha ahetuhi, ","tha-ap3:100.4":"sitam patukaronti te’. ","tha-ap3:101.1":"Anomadassi bhagava, ","tha-ap3:101.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap3:101.3":"Bhikkhumajjhe nisiditva, ","tha-ap3:101.4":"imam gatham abhasatha. ","tha-ap3:102.1":"‘Yo mam pupphena pujesi, ","tha-ap3:102.2":"nanancapi anutthavi; ","tha-ap3:102.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap3:102.4":"sunotha mama bhasato’. ","tha-ap3:103.1":"Buddhassa giramannaya, ","tha-ap3:103.2":"sabbe deva samagata; ","tha-ap3:103.3":"Saddhammam sotukama te, ","tha-ap3:103.4":"sambuddhamupasankamum. ","tha-ap3:104.1":"Dasasu lokadhatusu, ","tha-ap3:104.2":"devakaya mahiddhika; ","tha-ap3:104.3":"Saddhammam sotukama te, ","tha-ap3:104.4":"sambuddhamupasankamum. ","tha-ap3:105.1":"‘Hatthi assa ratha patti, ","tha-ap3:105.2":"sena ca caturangini; ","tha-ap3:105.3":"Parivaressantimam niccam, ","tha-ap3:105.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap3:106.1":"Satthituriyasahassani, ","tha-ap3:106.2":"bheriyo samalankata; ","tha-ap3:106.3":"Upatthissantimam niccam, ","tha-ap3:106.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap3:107.1":"Solasitthisahassani, ","tha-ap3:107.2":"nariyo samalankata; ","tha-ap3:107.3":"Vicittavatthabharana, ","tha-ap3:107.4":"amuttamanikundala. ","tha-ap3:108.1":"Alarapamha hasula, ","tha-ap3:108.2":"susanna tanumajjhima; ","tha-ap3:108.3":"Parivaressantimam niccam, ","tha-ap3:108.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap3:109.1":"Kappasatasahassani, ","tha-ap3:109.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap3:109.3":"Sahassakkhattum cakkavatti, ","tha-ap3:109.4":"raja ratthe bhavissati. ","tha-ap3:110.1":"Sahassakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap3:110.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap3:110.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap3:110.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap3:111.1":"Pacchime bhavasampatte, ","tha-ap3:111.2":"manussattam gamissati; ","tha-ap3:111.3":"Brahmani sariya nama, ","tha-ap3:111.4":"dharayissati kucchina. ","tha-ap3:112.1":"Matuya namagottena, ","tha-ap3:112.2":"pannayissatiyam naro; ","tha-ap3:112.3":"Sariputtoti namena, ","tha-ap3:112.4":"tikkhapanno bhavissati. ","tha-ap3:113.1":"Asitikoti chaddetva, ","tha-ap3:113.2":"pabbajissatikincano; ","tha-ap3:113.3":"Gavesanto santipadam, ","tha-ap3:113.4":"carissati mahim imam. ","tha-ap3:114.1":"Apparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap3:114.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap3:114.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap3:114.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap3:115.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap3:115.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap3:115.3":"Sariputtoti namena, ","tha-ap3:115.4":"hessati aggasavako. ","tha-ap3:116.1":"Ayam bhagirathi ganga, ","tha-ap3:116.2":"himavanta pabhavita; ","tha-ap3:116.3":"Mahasamuddamappeti, ","tha-ap3:116.4":"tappayanti mahodadhim. ","tha-ap3:117.1":"Tathevayam sariputto, ","tha-ap3:117.2":"sake tisu visarado; ","tha-ap3:117.3":"Pannaya paramim gantva, ","tha-ap3:117.4":"tappayissati panine. ","tha-ap3:118.1":"Himavantamupadaya, ","tha-ap3:118.2":"sagaranca mahodadhim; ","tha-ap3:118.3":"Etthantare yam pulinam, ","tha-ap3:118.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap3:119.1":"Tampi sakka asesena, ","tha-ap3:119.2":"sankhatum ganana yatha; ","tha-ap3:119.3":"Na tveva sariputtassa, ","tha-ap3:119.4":"pannayanto bhavissati. ","tha-ap3:120.1":"Lakkhe thapiyamanamhi, ","tha-ap3:120.2":"khiye gangaya valuka; ","tha-ap3:120.3":"Na tveva sariputtassa, ","tha-ap3:120.4":"pannayanto bhavissati. ","tha-ap3:121.1":"Mahasamudde umiyo, ","tha-ap3:121.2":"gananato asankhiya; ","tha-ap3:121.3":"Tatheva sariputtassa, ","tha-ap3:121.4":"pannayanto na hessati. ","tha-ap3:122.1":"Aradhayitva sambuddham, ","tha-ap3:122.2":"gotamam sakyapungavam; ","tha-ap3:122.3":"Pannaya paramim gantva, ","tha-ap3:122.4":"hessati aggasavako. ","tha-ap3:123.1":"Pavattitam dhammacakkam, ","tha-ap3:123.2":"sakyaputtena tadina; ","tha-ap3:123.3":"Anuvattessati samma, ","tha-ap3:123.4":"vassento dhammavutthiyo. ","tha-ap3:124.1":"Sabbametam abhinnaya, ","tha-ap3:124.2":"gotamo sakyapungavo; ","tha-ap3:124.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap3:124.4":"aggatthane thapessati’. ","tha-ap3:125.1":"Aho me sukatam kammam, ","tha-ap3:125.2":"anomadassissa satthuno; ","tha-ap3:125.3":"Yassaham karam katvana, ","tha-ap3:125.4":"sabbattha paramim gato. ","tha-ap3:126.1":"Aparimeyye katam kammam, ","tha-ap3:126.2":"phalam dassesi me idha; ","tha-ap3:126.3":"Sumutto saravegova, ","tha-ap3:126.4":"kilese jhapayim aham. ","tha-ap3:127.1":"Asankhatam gavesanto, ","tha-ap3:127.2":"nibbanam acalam padam; ","tha-ap3:127.3":"Vicinam titthiye sabbe, ","tha-ap3:127.4":"esaham samsarim bhave. ","tha-ap3:128.1":"Yathapi byadhito poso, ","tha-ap3:128.2":"pariyeseyya osadham; ","tha-ap3:128.3":"Vicineyya vanam sabbam, ","tha-ap3:128.4":"byadhito parimuttiya. ","tha-ap3:129.1":"Asankhatam gavesanto, ","tha-ap3:129.2":"nibbanam amatam padam; ","tha-ap3:129.3":"Abbokinnam pancasatam, ","tha-ap3:129.4":"pabbajim isipabbajam. ","tha-ap3:130.1":"Jatabharena bharito, ","tha-ap3:130.2":"ajinuttaranivasano; ","tha-ap3:130.3":"Abhinnaparamim gantva, ","tha-ap3:130.4":"brahmalokam agacchiham. ","tha-ap3:131.1":"Natthi bahirake suddhi, ","tha-ap3:131.2":"thapetva jinasasanam; ","tha-ap3:131.3":"Ye keci buddhima satta, ","tha-ap3:131.4":"sujjhanti jinasasane. ","tha-ap3:132.1":"Attakaramayam etam, ","tha-ap3:132.2":"nayidam itihitiham; ","tha-ap3:132.3":"Asankhatam gavesanto, ","tha-ap3:132.4":"kutitthe sancarim aham. ","tha-ap3:133.1":"Yatha saratthiko poso, ","tha-ap3:133.2":"kadalim chetvana phalaye; ","tha-ap3:133.3":"Na tattha saram vindeyya, ","tha-ap3:133.4":"sarena rittako hi so. ","tha-ap3:134.1":"Tatheva titthiya loke, ","tha-ap3:134.2":"nanaditthi bahujjana; ","tha-ap3:134.3":"Asankhatena rittase, ","tha-ap3:134.4":"sarena kadali yatha. ","tha-ap3:135.1":"Pacchime bhavasampatte, ","tha-ap3:135.2":"brahmabandhu ahosaham; ","tha-ap3:135.3":"Mahabhogam chaddetvana, ","tha-ap3:135.4":"pabbajim anagariyam”. ","tha-ap3:136.1":"Pathamabhanavaram. ","tha-ap3:137.1":"“Ajjhayako mantadharo, ","tha-ap3:137.2":"tinnam vedana paragu; ","tha-ap3:137.3":"Brahmano sancayo nama, ","tha-ap3:137.4":"tassa mule vasamaham. ","tha-ap3:138.1":"Savako te mahavira, ","tha-ap3:138.2":"assaji nama brahmano; ","tha-ap3:138.3":"Durasado uggatejo, ","tha-ap3:138.4":"pindaya carati tada. ","tha-ap3:139.1":"Tamaddasasim sappannam, ","tha-ap3:139.2":"munim mone samahitam; ","tha-ap3:139.3":"Santacittam mahanagam, ","tha-ap3:139.4":"suphullam padumam yatha. ","tha-ap3:140.1":"Disva me cittamuppajji, ","tha-ap3:140.2":"sudantam suddhamanasam; ","tha-ap3:140.3":"Usabham pavaram viram, ","tha-ap3:140.4":"arahayam bhavissati. ","tha-ap3:141.1":"Pasadiko iriyati, ","tha-ap3:141.2":"abhirupo susamvuto; ","tha-ap3:141.3":"Uttame damathe danto, ","tha-ap3:141.4":"amatadassi bhavissati. ","tha-ap3:142.1":"Yannunaham uttamattham, ","tha-ap3:142.2":"puccheyyam tutthamanasam; ","tha-ap3:142.3":"So me puttho kathessati, ","tha-ap3:142.4":"patipucchamaham tada. ","tha-ap3:143.1":"Pindapatam carantassa, ","tha-ap3:143.2":"pacchato agamasaham; ","tha-ap3:143.3":"Okasam patimanento, ","tha-ap3:143.4":"pucchitum amatam padam. ","tha-ap3:144.1":"Vithintare anuppattam, ","tha-ap3:144.2":"upagantvana pucchaham; ","tha-ap3:144.3":"‘Katham gottosi tvam vira, ","tha-ap3:144.4":"kassa sissosi marisa’. ","tha-ap3:145.1":"So me puttho viyakasi, ","tha-ap3:145.2":"asambhitova kesari; ","tha-ap3:145.3":"‘Buddho loke samuppanno, ","tha-ap3:145.4":"tassa sissomhi avuso’. ","tha-ap3:146.1":"‘Kidisam te mahavira, ","tha-ap3:146.2":"anujata mahayasa; ","tha-ap3:146.3":"Buddhassa sasanam dhammam, ","tha-ap3:146.4":"sadhu me kathayassu bho’. ","tha-ap3:147.1":"So me puttho kathi sabbam, ","tha-ap3:147.2":"gambhiram nipunam padam; ","tha-ap3:147.3":"Tanhasallassa hantaram, ","tha-ap3:147.4":"sabbadukkhapanudanam. ","tha-ap3:148.1":"‘Ye dhamma hetuppabhava, ","tha-ap3:148.2":"Tesam hetum tathagato aha; ","tha-ap3:148.3":"Tesanca yo nirodho, ","tha-ap3:148.4":"Evamvadi mahasamano’. ","tha-ap3:149.1":"Soham vissajjite panhe, ","tha-ap3:149.2":"pathamam phalamajjhagam; ","tha-ap3:149.3":"Virajo vimalo asim, ","tha-ap3:149.4":"sutvana jinasasanam. ","tha-ap3:150.1":"Sutvana munino vakyam, ","tha-ap3:150.2":"passitva dhammamuttamam; ","tha-ap3:150.3":"Pariyogalhasaddhammo, ","tha-ap3:150.4":"imam gathamabhasaham. ","tha-ap3:151.1":"‘Eseva dhammo yadi tavadeva, ","tha-ap3:151.2":"Paccabyatha padamasokam; ","tha-ap3:151.3":"Adittham abbhatitam, ","tha-ap3:151.4":"Bahukehi kappanahutehi’. ","tha-ap3:152.1":"Svaham dhammam gavesanto, ","tha-ap3:152.2":"kutitthe sancarim aham; ","tha-ap3:152.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","tha-ap3:152.4":"kalo me nappamajjitum. ","tha-ap3:153.1":"Tositoham assajina, ","tha-ap3:153.2":"patvana acalam padam; ","tha-ap3:153.3":"Sahayakam gavesanto, ","tha-ap3:153.4":"assamam agamasaham. ","tha-ap3:154.1":"Duratova mamam disva, ","tha-ap3:154.2":"sahayo me susikkhito; ","tha-ap3:154.3":"Iriyapathasampanno, ","tha-ap3:154.4":"idam vacanamabravi. ","tha-ap3:155.1":"‘Pasannamukhanettosi, ","tha-ap3:155.2":"munibhavova dissati; ","tha-ap3:155.3":"Amatadhigato kacci, ","tha-ap3:155.4":"nibbanamaccutam padam. ","tha-ap3:156.1":"Subhanurupo ayasi, ","tha-ap3:156.2":"anenjakarito viya; ","tha-ap3:156.3":"Dantova dantadamatho, ","tha-ap3:156.4":"upasantosi brahmana’. ","tha-ap3:157.1":"‘Amatam mayadhigatam, ","tha-ap3:157.2":"sokasallapanudanam; ","tha-ap3:157.3":"Tvampi tam adhigacchesi, ","tha-ap3:157.4":"gacchama buddhasantikam’. ","tha-ap3:158.1":"Sadhuti so patissutva, ","tha-ap3:158.2":"sahayo me susikkhito; ","tha-ap3:158.3":"Hatthena hattham ganhitva, ","tha-ap3:158.4":"upagamma tavantikam. ","tha-ap3:159.1":"Ubhopi pabbajissama, ","tha-ap3:159.2":"sakyaputta tavantike; ","tha-ap3:159.3":"Tava sasanamagamma, ","tha-ap3:159.4":"viharama anasava. ","tha-ap3:160.1":"Kolito iddhiya settho, ","tha-ap3:160.2":"aham pannaya parago; ","tha-ap3:160.3":"Ubhova ekato hutva, ","tha-ap3:160.4":"sasanam sobhayamase. ","tha-ap3:161.1":"Apariyositasankappo, ","tha-ap3:161.2":"kutitthe sancarim aham; ","tha-ap3:161.3":"Tava dassanamagamma, ","tha-ap3:161.4":"sankappo purito mama. ","tha-ap3:162.1":"Pathaviyam patitthaya, ","tha-ap3:162.2":"pupphanti samaye duma; ","tha-ap3:162.3":"Dibbagandha sampavanti, ","tha-ap3:162.4":"tosenti sabbapaninam. ","tha-ap3:163.1":"Tathevaham mahavira, ","tha-ap3:163.2":"sakyaputta mahayasa; ","tha-ap3:163.3":"Sasane te patitthaya, ","tha-ap3:163.4":"samayesami pupphitum. ","tha-ap3:164.1":"Vimuttipuppham esanto, ","tha-ap3:164.2":"bhavasamsaramocanam; ","tha-ap3:164.3":"Vimuttipupphalabhena, ","tha-ap3:164.4":"tosemi sabbapaninam. ","tha-ap3:165.1":"Yavata buddhakhettamhi, ","tha-ap3:165.2":"thapetvana mahamunim; ","tha-ap3:165.3":"Pannaya sadiso natthi, ","tha-ap3:165.4":"tava puttassa cakkhuma. ","tha-ap3:166.1":"Suvinita ca te sissa, ","tha-ap3:166.2":"parisa ca susikkhita; ","tha-ap3:166.3":"Uttame damathe danta, ","tha-ap3:166.4":"parivarenti tam sada. ","tha-ap3:167.1":"Jhayi jhanarata dhira, ","tha-ap3:167.2":"santacitta samahita; ","tha-ap3:167.3":"Muni moneyyasampanna, ","tha-ap3:167.4":"parivarenti tam sada. ","tha-ap3:168.1":"Appiccha nipaka dhira, ","tha-ap3:168.2":"appahara alolupa; ","tha-ap3:168.3":"Labhalabhena santuttha, ","tha-ap3:168.4":"parivarenti tam sada. ","tha-ap3:169.1":"Arannika dhutarata, ","tha-ap3:169.2":"jhayino lukhacivara; ","tha-ap3:169.3":"Vivekabhirata dhira, ","tha-ap3:169.4":"parivarenti tam sada. ","tha-ap3:170.1":"Patipanna phalattha ca, ","tha-ap3:170.2":"sekha phalasamangino; ","tha-ap3:170.3":"Asisaka uttamattham, ","tha-ap3:170.4":"parivarenti tam sada. ","tha-ap3:171.1":"Sotapanna ca vimala, ","tha-ap3:171.2":"sakadagamino ca ye; ","tha-ap3:171.3":"Anagami ca araha, ","tha-ap3:171.4":"parivarenti tam sada. ","tha-ap3:172.1":"Satipatthanakusala, ","tha-ap3:172.2":"bojjhangabhavanarata; ","tha-ap3:172.3":"Savaka te bahu sabbe, ","tha-ap3:172.4":"parivarenti tam sada. ","tha-ap3:173.1":"Iddhipadesu kusala, ","tha-ap3:173.2":"samadhibhavanarata; ","tha-ap3:173.3":"Sammappadhananuyutta, ","tha-ap3:173.4":"parivarenti tam sada. ","tha-ap3:174.1":"Tevijja chalabhinna ca, ","tha-ap3:174.2":"iddhiya paramim gata; ","tha-ap3:174.3":"Pannaya paramim patta, ","tha-ap3:174.4":"parivarenti tam sada. ","tha-ap3:175.1":"Edisa te mahavira, ","tha-ap3:175.2":"tava sissa susikkhita; ","tha-ap3:175.3":"Durasada uggateja, ","tha-ap3:175.4":"parivarenti tam sada. ","tha-ap3:176.1":"Tehi sissehi parivuto, ","tha-ap3:176.2":"sannatehi tapassibhi; ","tha-ap3:176.3":"Migarajavasambhito, ","tha-ap3:176.4":"ulurajava sobhasi. ","tha-ap3:177.1":"Pathaviyam patitthaya, ","tha-ap3:177.2":"ruhanti dharaniruha; ","tha-ap3:177.3":"Vepullatam papunanti, ","tha-ap3:177.4":"phalanca dassayanti te. ","tha-ap3:178.1":"Pathavisadiso tvamsi, ","tha-ap3:178.2":"sakyaputta mahayasa; ","tha-ap3:178.3":"Sasane te patitthaya, ","tha-ap3:178.4":"labhanti amatam phalam. ","tha-ap3:179.1":"Sindhu sarassati ceva, ","tha-ap3:179.2":"nadiyo candabhagika; ","tha-ap3:179.3":"Ganga ca yamuna ceva, ","tha-ap3:179.4":"sarabhu ca atho mahi. ","tha-ap3:180.1":"Etasam sandamananam, ","tha-ap3:180.2":"sagaro sampaticchati; ","tha-ap3:180.3":"Jahanti purimam namam, ","tha-ap3:180.4":"sagaroteva nayati. ","tha-ap3:181.1":"Tathevime catubbanna, ","tha-ap3:181.2":"pabbajitva tavantike; ","tha-ap3:181.3":"Jahanti purimam namam, ","tha-ap3:181.4":"buddhaputtati nayare. ","tha-ap3:182.1":"Yathapi cando vimalo, ","tha-ap3:182.2":"gaccham akasadhatuya; ","tha-ap3:182.3":"Sabbe taragane loke, ","tha-ap3:182.4":"abhaya atirocati. ","tha-ap3:183.1":"Tatheva tvam mahavira, ","tha-ap3:183.2":"parivuto devamanuse; ","tha-ap3:183.3":"Ete sabbe atikkamma, ","tha-ap3:183.4":"jalasi sabbada tuvam. ","tha-ap3:184.1":"Gambhire utthita umi, ","tha-ap3:184.2":"na velamativattare; ","tha-ap3:184.3":"Sabba velamva phusanti, ","tha-ap3:184.4":"sancunna vikiranti ta. ","tha-ap3:185.1":"Tatheva titthiya loke, ","tha-ap3:185.2":"nanaditthi bahujjana; ","tha-ap3:185.3":"Dhammam vaditukama te, ","tha-ap3:185.4":"nativattanti tam munim. ","tha-ap3:186.1":"Sace ca tam papunanti, ","tha-ap3:186.2":"pativadehi cakkhuma; ","tha-ap3:186.3":"Tavantikam upagantva, ","tha-ap3:186.4":"sancunnava bhavanti te. ","tha-ap3:187.1":"Yathapi udake jata, ","tha-ap3:187.2":"kumuda mandalaka bahu; ","tha-ap3:187.3":"Upalimpanti toyena, ","tha-ap3:187.4":"kaddamakalalena ca. ","tha-ap3:188.1":"Tatheva bahuka satta, ","tha-ap3:188.2":"loke jata viruhare; ","tha-ap3:188.3":"Attita ragadosena, ","tha-ap3:188.4":"kaddame kumudam yatha. ","tha-ap3:189.1":"Yathapi padumam jalajam, ","tha-ap3:189.2":"jalamajjhe viruhati; ","tha-ap3:189.3":"Na so limpati toyena, ","tha-ap3:189.4":"parisuddho hi kesari. ","tha-ap3:190.1":"Tatheva tvam mahavira, ","tha-ap3:190.2":"loke jato mahamuni; ","tha-ap3:190.3":"Nopalimpasi lokena, ","tha-ap3:190.4":"toyena padumam yatha. ","tha-ap3:191.1":"Yathapi rammake mase, ","tha-ap3:191.2":"bahu pupphanti varija; ","tha-ap3:191.3":"Natikkamanti tam masam, ","tha-ap3:191.4":"samayo pupphanaya so. ","tha-ap3:192.1":"Tatheva tvam mahavira, ","tha-ap3:192.2":"pupphito te vimuttiya; ","tha-ap3:192.3":"Sasanam nativattanti, ","tha-ap3:192.4":"padumam varijam yatha. ","tha-ap3:193.1":"Supupphito salaraja, ","tha-ap3:193.2":"dibbagandham pavayati; ","tha-ap3:193.3":"Annasalehi parivuto, ","tha-ap3:193.4":"salarajava sobhati. ","tha-ap3:194.1":"Tatheva tvam mahavira, ","tha-ap3:194.2":"buddhananena pupphito; ","tha-ap3:194.3":"Bhikkhusanghaparivuto, ","tha-ap3:194.4":"salarajava sobhasi. ","tha-ap3:195.1":"Yathapi selo himava, ","tha-ap3:195.2":"osadho sabbapaninam; ","tha-ap3:195.3":"Naganam asurananca, ","tha-ap3:195.4":"devatananca alayo. ","tha-ap3:196.1":"Tatheva tvam mahavira, ","tha-ap3:196.2":"osadho viya paninam; ","tha-ap3:196.3":"Tevijja chalabhinna ca, ","tha-ap3:196.4":"iddhiya paramim gata. ","tha-ap3:197.1":"Anusittha mahavira, ","tha-ap3:197.2":"taya karunikena te; ","tha-ap3:197.3":"Ramanti dhammaratiya, ","tha-ap3:197.4":"vasanti tava sasane. ","tha-ap3:198.1":"Migaraja yatha siho, ","tha-ap3:198.2":"abhinikkhamma asaya; ","tha-ap3:198.3":"Catuddisanuviloketva, ","tha-ap3:198.4":"tikkhattum abhinadati. ","tha-ap3:199.1":"Sabbe miga uttasanti, ","tha-ap3:199.2":"migarajassa gajjato; ","tha-ap3:199.3":"Tatha hi jatima eso, ","tha-ap3:199.4":"pasu taseti sabbada. ","tha-ap3:200.1":"Gajjato te mahavira, ","tha-ap3:200.2":"vasudha sampakampati; ","tha-ap3:200.3":"Bodhaneyyavabujjhanti, ","tha-ap3:200.4":"tasanti marakayika. ","tha-ap3:201.1":"Tasanti titthiya sabbe, ","tha-ap3:201.2":"nadato te mahamuni; ","tha-ap3:201.3":"Kaka senava vibbhanta, ","tha-ap3:201.4":"migaranna yatha miga. ","tha-ap3:202.1":"Ye keci ganino loke, ","tha-ap3:202.2":"sattharoti pavuccare; ","tha-ap3:202.3":"Paramparagatam dhammam, ","tha-ap3:202.4":"desenti parisaya te. ","tha-ap3:203.1":"Na hevam tvam mahavira, ","tha-ap3:203.2":"dhammam desesi paninam; ","tha-ap3:203.3":"Samam saccani bujjhitva, ","tha-ap3:203.4":"kevalam bodhipakkhiyam. ","tha-ap3:204.1":"Asayanusayam natva, ","tha-ap3:204.2":"indriyanam balabalam; ","tha-ap3:204.3":"Bhabbabhabbe viditvana, ","tha-ap3:204.4":"mahameghova gajjasi. ","tha-ap3:205.1":"Cakkavalapariyanta, ","tha-ap3:205.2":"nisinna parisa bhave; ","tha-ap3:205.3":"Nanaditthi vicinanta, ","tha-ap3:205.4":"vimaticchedanaya tam. ","tha-ap3:206.1":"Sabbesam cittamannaya, ","tha-ap3:206.2":"opammakusalo muni; ","tha-ap3:206.3":"Ekam panham kathentova, ","tha-ap3:206.4":"vimatim chindasi paninam. ","tha-ap3:207.1":"Upatissasadiseheva, ","tha-ap3:207.2":"vasudha purita bhave; ","tha-ap3:207.3":"Sabbeva te panjalika, ","tha-ap3:207.4":"kittayum lokanayakam. ","tha-ap3:208.1":"Kappam va te kittayanta, ","tha-ap3:208.2":"nanavannehi kittayum; ","tha-ap3:208.3":"Parimetum na sakkeyyum, ","tha-ap3:208.4":"appameyyo tathagato. ","tha-ap3:209.1":"Yathasakena thamena, ","tha-ap3:209.2":"kittito hi maya jino; ","tha-ap3:209.3":"Kappakotipi kittenta, ","tha-ap3:209.4":"evamevam pakittayum. ","tha-ap3:210.1":"Sace hi koci devo va, ","tha-ap3:210.2":"manusso va susikkhito; ","tha-ap3:210.3":"Pametum parikappeyya, ","tha-ap3:210.4":"vighatamva labheyya so. ","tha-ap3:211.1":"Sasane te patitthaya, ","tha-ap3:211.2":"sakyaputta mahayasa; ","tha-ap3:211.3":"Pannaya paramim gantva, ","tha-ap3:211.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap3:212.1":"Titthiye sampamaddami, ","tha-ap3:212.2":"vattemi jinasasanam; ","tha-ap3:212.3":"Dhammasenapati ajja, ","tha-ap3:212.4":"sakyaputtassa sasane. ","tha-ap3:213.1":"Aparimeyye katam kammam, ","tha-ap3:213.2":"phalam dassesi me idha; ","tha-ap3:213.3":"Sukhitto saravegova, ","tha-ap3:213.4":"kilese jhapayi mama. ","tha-ap3:214.1":"Yo koci manujo bharam, ","tha-ap3:214.2":"dhareyya matthake sada; ","tha-ap3:214.3":"Bharena dukkhito assa, ","tha-ap3:214.4":"bharehi bharito tatha. ","tha-ap3:215.1":"Dayhamano tihaggihi, ","tha-ap3:215.2":"bhavesu samsarim aham; ","tha-ap3:215.3":"Bharito bhavabharena, ","tha-ap3:215.4":"girim uccarito yatha. ","tha-ap3:216.1":"Oropito ca me bharo, ","tha-ap3:216.2":"bhava ugghatita maya; ","tha-ap3:216.3":"Karaniyam katam sabbam, ","tha-ap3:216.4":"sakyaputtassa sasane. ","tha-ap3:217.1":"Yavata buddhakhettamhi, ","tha-ap3:217.2":"thapetva sakyapungavam; ","tha-ap3:217.3":"Aham aggomhi pannaya, ","tha-ap3:217.4":"sadiso me na vijjati. ","tha-ap3:218.1":"Samadhimhi sukusalo, ","tha-ap3:218.2":"iddhiya paramim gato; ","tha-ap3:218.3":"Icchamano caham ajja, ","tha-ap3:218.4":"sahassam abhinimmine. ","tha-ap3:219.1":"Anupubbaviharassa, ","tha-ap3:219.2":"vasibhuto mahamuni; ","tha-ap3:219.3":"Kathesi sasanam mayham, ","tha-ap3:219.4":"nirodho sayanam mama. ","tha-ap3:220.1":"Dibbacakkhu visuddham me, ","tha-ap3:220.2":"samadhikusalo aham; ","tha-ap3:220.3":"Sammappadhananuyutto, ","tha-ap3:220.4":"bojjhangabhavanarato. ","tha-ap3:221.1":"Savakena hi pattabbam, ","tha-ap3:221.2":"sabbameva katam maya; ","tha-ap3:221.3":"Lokanatham thapetvana, ","tha-ap3:221.4":"sadiso me na vijjati. ","tha-ap3:222.1":"Samapattinam kusalo, ","tha-ap3:222.2":"Jhanavimokkhana khippapatilabhi; ","tha-ap3:222.3":"Bojjhangabhavanarato, ","tha-ap3:222.4":"Savakagunaparamigatosmi. ","tha-ap3:223.1":"Savakagunenapi phussena, ","tha-ap3:223.2":"Buddhiya parisuttamabharava; ","tha-ap3:223.3":"Yam saddhasangahitam cittam, ","tha-ap3:223.4":"Sada sabrahmacarisu. ","tha-ap3:224.1":"Uddhatavisova sappo, ","tha-ap3:224.2":"Chinnavisanova usabho; ","tha-ap3:224.3":"Nikkhittamanadappova, ","tha-ap3:224.4":"Upemi garugaravena ganam. ","tha-ap3:225.1":"Yadi rupini bhaveyya, ","tha-ap3:225.2":"Panna me vasumatipi na sameyya; ","tha-ap3:225.3":"Anomadassissa bhagavato, ","tha-ap3:225.4":"Phalametam nanathavanaya. ","tha-ap3:226.1":"Pavattitam dhammacakkam, ","tha-ap3:226.2":"sakyaputtena tadina; ","tha-ap3:226.3":"Anuvattemaham samma, ","tha-ap3:226.4":"nanathavanayidam phalam. ","tha-ap3:227.1":"Ma me kadaci papiccho, ","tha-ap3:227.2":"kusito hinaviriyo; ","tha-ap3:227.3":"Appassuto anacaro, ","tha-ap3:227.4":"sameto ahu katthaci. ","tha-ap3:228.1":"Bahussuto ca medhavi, ","tha-ap3:228.2":"silesu susamahito; ","tha-ap3:228.3":"Cetosamathanuyutto, ","tha-ap3:228.4":"api muddhani titthatu. ","tha-ap3:229.1":"Tam vo vadami bhaddante, ","tha-ap3:229.2":"yavantettha samagata; ","tha-ap3:229.3":"Appiccha hotha santuttha, ","tha-ap3:229.4":"jhayi jhanarata sada. ","tha-ap3:230.1":"Yamaham pathamam disva, ","tha-ap3:230.2":"virajo vimalo ahum; ","tha-ap3:230.3":"So me acariyo dhiro, ","tha-ap3:230.4":"assaji nama savako. ","tha-ap3:231.1":"Tassaham vahasa ajja, ","tha-ap3:231.2":"dhammasenapati ahum; ","tha-ap3:231.3":"Sabbattha paramim patva, ","tha-ap3:231.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap3:232.1":"Yo me acariyo asi, ","tha-ap3:232.2":"assaji nama savako; ","tha-ap3:232.3":"Yassam disayam vasati, ","tha-ap3:232.4":"ussisamhi karomaham. ","tha-ap3:233.1":"Mama kammam saritvana, ","tha-ap3:233.2":"gotamo sakyapungavo; ","tha-ap3:233.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap3:233.4":"aggatthane thapesi mam. ","tha-ap3:234.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap3:234.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap3:234.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap3:234.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap3:235.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap3:235.2":"buddhasetthassa santike; ","tha-ap3:235.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap3:235.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap3:236.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap3:236.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap3:236.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap3:236.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap3:237.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sariputto thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap3:238.1":"Sariputtattherassapadanam pathamam. "}